

structure of project  && creation of project

                                                      Project Creation


1. Create new project (Dynamic web project)
3. Remove build path(src\java\main) and create src file - java code
4. Remove web path(webpages) and create WebContent - jsp, xml
5. Create lib folder inside WEB-INF
6. Create view folder inside WEB-INF
7. Create servlet(anyname).xml for mapping inside WEB-INF
8. Create web.xml for IOC,Validation,formating,mvc-annotation inside WEB-INF
9. Add JSTL1,JSTL2 jar file inside lib and  spring jar file
10.Create .jsp page inside view folder.